{"tid":239119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七一維穩】彭博：中央設「港股穩定計劃」 資金隨時入市","createTime":"2017-05-11T12:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T19:14:28.000Z","uid":113790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b27c106f2a23b38b0c7676412deccfc5b1c18e5","tid":239119,"uid":113790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"彭博引述消息指，內地已制定七一前，穩定港股計劃，以便中央政府領導層訪港、以及新一任特首就職時，製造良好氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道指，該計劃有一些中資背景公司具體執行，所需資金已經準備就緒，如有需要，這些資金可以入市；但尚不清楚這些資金在何種情況下會入市。<br />\n<br />\n港交所（388）發言人拒評市場傳聞。發言人同時補充，任何交易都應依市場規例，操縱市場屬違法，會受《證券及期貨條例》規管及處分。證監會發言人不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170511&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=56680140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170511%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D56680140&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=996b644a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170511%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D56680140&h=162c26e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170511&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=56680140</a><br />\n【七一維穩】彭博：中央設「港股穩定計劃」 資金隨時入市"},{"pid":"2ba7332f4ec1832e1941c88bb2953008802d3f40","tid":239119,"uid":113790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"自膠 開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都要屌中共老母"},{"pid":"861a977f042625c9b3a5f2de2f5040de7f3e7671","tid":239119,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"佢搞掂自己個上證先啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cade06499e146716e36ead4ba36fabc71797068","tid":239119,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:14:28.000Z","msg":"干預市場，仲要支那熱錢<br />\n一定爆泡爆到仆街"}]}